                                        </button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <figure class="image">
                                    <img src="starbucks_slider/static/src/img/3.png" alt="Doppio espresso" />
                                    <figcaption>Doppio espresso, a new product</figcaption>
                                </figure>
                            </article>
                            <article class="item">
                                <div class="main-content"
